{"tid":2347336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍2驅逐艦航經台海 中國國防部：堅決反對挑釁攪局","createTime":"2020-12-31T03:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T06:49:16.000Z","uid":337052,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f9ba7b4aa942d2c7aaebdb149354f6e921967a","tid":2347336,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:26:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">美軍2驅逐艦航經台海 中國國防部：挑釁攪局</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/12/31 10:52<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北31日電）<span class=\"red\">美軍飛彈驅逐艦馬侃號（USS John S. McCain）與魏柏號（USS Curtis Wilbur） 今天上午由南向北航經台灣海峽。中國國防部指美艦「炫耀武力，挑釁攪局」，危害台海地區和平穩定。</span><br />\n<br />\n中華民國國防部表示，美軍2艘驅逐艦上午由南海航經台灣海峽後，向北航行，國軍全程掌握。這是美國軍艦今年第13度通過台灣海峽。<br />\n<br />\n中國國防部上午也透過官方微博帳號「國防部發布」發表聲明指，中國人民解放軍組織海空兵力全程對美艦進行跟蹤監視。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，這是美艦18日後再次穿航台灣海峽，<span class=\"red\">「炫耀武力，挑釁攪局」</span>，並稱<span class=\"red\">「美艦行徑對『台獨』勢力傳遞錯誤信號，嚴重危害台海地區和平穩定，我們對此表示堅決反對」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，共軍時刻保持高度戒備，隨時應對一切威脅挑釁，堅決捍衛國家主權和領土完整。（編輯：沈朋達/周慧盈）1091231<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202012310054.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202012310054.aspx&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm5dwtLMCc893KahbJtTxKsc%3D&h=51ded88c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202012310054.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/12/31/realtime/10394994.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F12%2F31%2Frealtime%2F10394994.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=04a3c9cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為美國飛彈驅逐艦馬侃號資料照。歐新社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.litenews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/%E5%90%B3%E8%AC%99_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litenews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F%25E5%2590%25B3%25E8%25AC%2599_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.png&h=a8e4641c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國防部新聞發言人吳謙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/1231/U617P22T1D870986F1DT20201231102620.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2020%2F1231%2FU617P22T1D870986F1DT20201231102620.png&h=4bde3c28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6066fa8d491c017c2d27430e6372d3c3cea3ada","tid":2347336,"uid":214309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"大和田呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ffb53b91b02bf9bbb0845468b20d784b26d5ab","tid":2347336,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/_UYPToBs3ebXOZd5WZmP34Jhvzs=/760x542/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WOX5PHDF5VAPUZEGDWSLTOJOOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_UYPToBs3ebXOZd5WZmP34Jhvzs%3D%2F760x542%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWOX5PHDF5VAPUZEGDWSLTOJOOU.jpg&h=da32a90b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柏克級神盾驅逐艦「柯蒂斯魏柏號」今再通過台灣海峽。翻攝美國海軍網站資料照片<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍兩艘軍艦今（12/31）航經台灣海峽，是美軍軍艦本月第二度、今年第13度航經台海，美國海軍表示此舉符合國際法，是「展現美國對自由與開放印太地區的承諾」。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍宣布，導向飛彈驅逐艦麥肯號（USS John S. McCain）與柯蒂斯魏柏號（USS Curtis Wilbur）「12月31日依據國際法例行航經台灣海峽」，「展現美國對自由與開放印太地區的承諾」。聲明指，美軍將持續在國際法允許之處執行飛行、航行及其他任務。"},{"pid":"664fd2913b752a5c2b0a3eb07be99a13ca5524c9","tid":2347336,"uid":158270,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T03:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K2kYP6b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK2kYP6b.gif&h=790a1299&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64f